{"tid":1559111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普突炒國安顧問博爾頓 稱在多項議題存「強烈分歧」","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:40.000Z","uid":68738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df1211de159718d725d622c6737186eed12ea35e","tid":1559111,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190911/large/1568132367_b7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568132367_b7b9.jpg&h=c33acc32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普稱與博爾頓意見不合。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周二在Twitter宣佈，以意見不合為由炒掉國家安全顧問博爾頓（John Bolton）。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在推文寫道：「我昨晚通知博爾頓白宮不再需要他的服務。我對他多項建議強烈不同意。」他表示下周會提名人選填補空缺。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190911/60031788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60031788&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRekPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=4c34d25f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60031788&h=fffbf6fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190911/60031788</a>"},{"pid":"122b2c181292cecc7ec65e24d59b93e783aee029","tid":1559111,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4a8ed39f678d0569fc2ac90130c43b809307d2","tid":1559111,"uid":265061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"屌 咩料"},{"pid":"2121dbdb23c3ebb5d33d05ea406faa6c8676b8bc","tid":1559111,"uid":6